meta.job_title: Travel Nurse RN Med Surg / Telemetry

duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide exceptional patient care in the Med Surg / Telemetry unit.
Collaborate with healthcare teams to ensure patient well-being and recovery.
Read and interpret telemetry readings to monitor patients' conditions.
Ensure compliance with BLS certification requirements and protocols.

education_certification.credential: Bachelor's degree in Nursing or related field (Master's preferred)
